  "identifier": "SB 88",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to protection from extreme weather conditions.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 278 to define terms and require a utility to submit a disconnection plan to the Public Service Commission that prohibits the utility from suspending residential service during extreme weather conditions; make the disconnection plan available on both the commission and the utility's website.",
